00:39.963 --> 00:44.669
There are 24 hours in a day, and seven days in a week.

00:45.146 --> 00:53.201
When you say twenty-four seven in a conversation, it refers to 24 hours a day, 7 days a week.

00:53.691 --> 00:58.590
It is another way of saying all day and all night, every day of the week.

00:58.781 --> 01:00.589
And that's English in a Minute.

